                    "sceneId": "e8520824-d970-4c6e-8aec-6c308c8846ab",
                    "propId": "6fdd5328-909a-40a3-8b6a-5d9feae40b4d",
                    "target": "1",
                    "notify": false
                },
                {
                    "type": "nodes.changeReputation",
                    "id": "1f0f65f3-b61c-486b-818d-a74d0749bffd",
                    "actorId": "59d4db68-0e1f-4cca-8118-eb49edcf3859",
                    "amount": "3",
                    "change": "1",
                    "notify": false
                },
                {
                    "type": "nodes.speak",
                    "id": "2cd5f8a1-0007-429b-8334-f6e46fd15552",
                    "actorId": "59d4db68-0e1f-4cca-8118-eb49edcf3859",
                    "actorId2": null,
                    "text": "Welcome back to a new session of <i>Magic for Mundanes.</i> I am certain that you are all as thrilled as I would be to again study the mystical manipulation of the forces that surround us.",
                    "emotion": "1",
                    "emotion2": "0",
                    "device": "0",
                    "device2": "0"
                },
                {
                    "type": "nodes.speak",
                    "id": "9f6fcec3-b518-437f-8a06-a0446a15227f",
                    "actorId": "59d4db68-0e1f-4cca-8118-eb49edcf3859",
                    "actorId2": null,
                    "text": "I do hope that you have found your lessons and runestones from the first session useful. I also hope that you have been practicing your Sense Magic spell whenever possible... It will build up your Magic skill and Mojo.",
                    "emotion": "1",
                    "emotion2": "0",
                    "device": "0",
                    "device2": "0"
                },
                {
                    "type": "nodes.speak",
                    "id": "244c180e-6b44-4081-b3ff-bb9930035afb",
                    "actorId": "59d4db68-0e1f-4cca-8118-eb49edcf3859",
                    "actorId2": null,
                    "text": "We will begin this second elective with a brief lecture on the major Aspects of magic - Alchemy, Sorcery, Enchantment, Conjuration, and Necromancy.",
                    "emotion": "0",
                    "emotion2": "0",
                    "device": "0",
                    "device2": "0"
                },
                {
                    "type": "nodes.speak",
                    "id": "8608c86f-60d0-4cad-becd-e2b905f4da17",
                    "actorId": "59d4db68-0e1f-4cca-8118-eb49edcf3859",
                    "actorId2": null,
                    "text": "Are there any questions or comments before I begin the lecture?",
                    "emotion": "0",
                    "emotion2": "0",
                    "device": "0",
                    "device2": "0"
                },
                {
                    "id": "7c4c554a-044f-4c1f-90b8-8d76576cee8c",
                    "type": "nodes.improveSkill",
                    "skill": "Magic",
                    "amount": "2",
                    "notify": true
                },
                {
                    "type": "nodes.showMenu",
                    "id": "a24bc584-9c2b-4af0-81b2-13a91bfc064d",
                    "options": [
                        {
                            "type": "options.text",
                            "id": "33186445-d4cb-4a0b-9bf8-3edf72078dd8",
                            "text": "Say Something Polite About the Class",
                            "nodes": [
                                {
                                    "id": "6e22c72e-3479-4864-a438-e205107952dc",
                                    "type": "nodes.skillBranch",
                                    "skill": "Charm",
                                    "target": "43",
                                    "success": {
                                        "type": "nodes.block",
                                        "nodes": []
                                    },
                                    "failure": {
                                        "type": "nodes.block",
                                        "nodes": []
                                    },
                                    "notify": true
                                },
                                {
                                    "type": "nodes.speak",
                                    "id": "9229e005-5da8-42d8-b9a4-67a8fdee324b",
                                    "actorId": "30ee2636-15e3-452e-a2db-09cbb9012970",
                                    "actorId2": "59d4db68-0e1f-4cca-8118-eb49edcf3859",
                                    "text": "I just want to say how good it is to get back to this class. There's nothing quite like teatime to refresh the body and Magic to refresh the mind.",
                                    "emotion": "1",
                                    "emotion2": "1",
                                    "device": "0",
                                    "device2": "0"
                                },
                                {
                                    "type": "nodes.changeReputation",
                                    "id": "a9c42f44-7d5f-41af-a318-5fd5f2adca60",
                                    "actorId": "59d4db68-0e1f-4cca-8118-eb49edcf3859",
                                    "amount": "2",
                                    "change": "1",
                                    "notify": true
                                },
                                {
                                    "type": "nodes.speak",
                                    "id": "92056ffc-4bf4-4c85-9ef8-7dedb6ec3a5d",
                                    "actorId": "59d4db68-0e1f-4cca-8118-eb49edcf3859",
                                    "actorId2": "30ee2636-15e3-452e-a2db-09cbb9012970",
                                    "text": "Indeed, Mr. O'Conner, indeed.",
                                    "emotion": "1",
                                    "emotion2": "1",
                                    "device": "0",
                                    "device2": "0"
                                }
                            ],
                            "expression": null,
                            "ignoreChildAvailability": false,
                            "minutes": "3",
                            "ExitMenu": true
                        },
                        {
                            "type": "options.text",
                            "id": "01c63818-ff6c-4bea-b03c-0f3b95be7f98",
                            "text": "Ask About the Usefulness of the Class",
                            "nodes": [
                                {
                                    "type": "nodes.speak",
                                    "id": "f3454a09-0318-4944-9cdd-f50fec567074",
                                    "actorId": "30ee2636-15e3-452e-a2db-09cbb9012970",
                                    "actorId2": "59d4db68-0e1f-4cca-8118-eb49edcf3859",
                                    "text": "Will we be making more Combat runestones and other items? The runestones we made in the last class were very useful.",
                                    "emotion": "0",
                                    "emotion2": "0",
                                    "device": "0",
                                    "device2": "0"
                                },
                                {
                                    "type": "nodes.speak",
                                    "id": "69e17f90-f9f2-41ed-99ea-2b6c1d7810ef",
                                    "actorId": "59d4db68-0e1f-4cca-8118-eb49edcf3859",
                                    "actorId2": "30ee2636-15e3-452e-a2db-09cbb9012970",
                                    "text": "Yes, this class session will primarily focus on the practical application of magic. However, a little background information from this lecture will provide the foundation of understanding as to why and how we do things.",
                                    "emotion": "1",
                                    "emotion2": "0",
                                    "device": "0",
                                    "device2": "0"
                                }
                            ],
                            "expression": null,
                            "ignoreChildAvailability": false,
                            "minutes": "4",
                            "ExitMenu": true
                        },
                        {
                            "type": "options.text",
                            "id": "94fb3e05-8a79-4665-99cd-57b555bbc7f6",
                            "text": "Make a Joke",
                            "nodes": [
                                {
                                    "id": "7eb502e4-06c1-4108-9983-656e8f651abc",
                                    "type": "nodes.skillBranch",
                                    "skill": "Moxie",
                                    "target": "43",
                                    "success": {
                                        "type": "nodes.block",
                                        "nodes": []
                                    },
                                    "failure": {
                                        "type": "nodes.block",
                                        "nodes": [
                                            {
                                                "type": "nodes.changeReputation",
                                                "id": "b2b7e964-38ec-4e22-ac7d-689b5a49938c",
                                                "actorId": "59d4db68-0e1f-4cca-8118-eb49edcf3859",
                                                "amount": "1",
                                                "change": "0",
                                                "notify": true
                                            }
                                        ]
                                    },
                                    "notify": true
                                },
                                {
                                    "type": "nodes.speak",
                                    "id": "7932f813-1caa-43dc-beca-f868974c4541",
                                    "actorId": "30ee2636-15e3-452e-a2db-09cbb9012970",
                                    "actorId2": "59d4db68-0e1f-4cca-8118-eb49edcf3859",
                                    "text": "Do you know why the lonely Wizard summoned the Zombie of his lost love?",
                                    "emotion": "1",
                                    "emotion2": "4",
                                    "device": "0",
                                    "device2": "0"
                                },
                                {
                                    "type": "nodes.speak",
                                    "id": "4b6c9629-1c43-4992-8f6c-7879a56c48c6",
                                    "actorId": "59d4db68-0e1f-4cca-8118-eb49edcf3859",
                                    "actorId2": "30ee2636-15e3-452e-a2db-09cbb9012970",
                                    "text": "I don't really know the lonely Wizard to whom you refer, so I cannot answer your question.",
                                    "emotion": "0",
                                    "emotion2": "1",
                                    "device": "0",
                                    "device2": "0"
                                },
                                {
                                    "type": "nodes.speak",
                                    "id": "428234f2-0ce1-456d-82ad-7bce6254f019",
                                    "actorId": "30ee2636-15e3-452e-a2db-09cbb9012970",
                                    "actorId2": "59d4db68-0e1f-4cca-8118-eb49edcf3859",
                                    "text": "Because he wanted to put the romance back into Necromancy.",
                                    "emotion": "1",
                                    "emotion2": "4",
                                    "device": "0",
                                    "device2": "0"
                                },
                                {
                                    "type": "nodes.speak",
                                    "id": "a98c1ab4-4901-428a-8087-52bd4b3b8482",
                                    "actorId": "59d4db68-0e1f-4cca-8118-eb49edcf3859",
                                    "actorId2": "30ee2636-15e3-452e-a2db-09cbb9012970",
                                    "text": "Mr. O'Conner, could you please refrain from such diversions so that we can focus upon lecture?",
                                    "emotion": "0",
                                    "emotion2": "1",
                                    "device": "0",
                                    "device2": "0"
                                }
                            ],
                            "expression": null,
                            "ignoreChildAvailability": false,
                            "minutes": "4",
                            "ExitMenu": true
                        },
                        {
                            "type": "options.text",
                            "id": "4d52d549-1dee-4b4c-8f94-18fc87b6a086",
                            "text": "Say Nothing",
                            "nodes": [],
                            "expression": null,
                            "ignoreChildAvailability": false,
                            "minutes": 0,
                            "ExitMenu": true
                        }
                    ],
                    "AutoAddDone": false,
                    "Unique": true
                },
                {
                    "type": "nodes.speak",
                    "id": "f977033d-5c98-4bef-8a45-ef8852600bb5",
                    "actorId": "59d4db68-0e1f-4cca-8118-eb49edcf3859",
                    "actorId2": null,
                    "text": "Wizardry, as you should know by now, is the study and application of symbols and runes to manipulate magic. There are many facets to Wizardry that focus on a particular methodology...",
                    "emotion": "0",
                    "emotion2": "0",
                    "device": "0",
